Review Text: Really nice coffee place. Nice service. It is really cool that they have 100% compostable cups!

Name: De Bakkerswinkel
Review Text: I go there every time I'm visiting Amsterdam. Not touristic and crowded. Friendly staff and really (really) amazing handmade cakes. I think I've tried most of them, and the chocolate one is still my favorite. ‚Ä¶

Name: De Bakkerswinkel
Review Text: Greatest sausage rolls of all time. Cooked to perfection, crispy pastry on the outside that crumbles with every bite, flavoursome moist filling and the perfect size for a snack. You must visit when in town.

Review Text: Wonderful place to start your day @Amsterdam. Perfect sandwiches!

Review Text: Love love love the Bakkerswinkel. Delicious breakfast food at a reasonable price. The scones are to die for, the sandwiches and chai latte are wonderful as well!
